text: Oluf Landnes (February 21, 1874 - April 21, 1911) was an American gymnast. He competed in four events at the 1904 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1874 births Category:1911 deaths Category:American male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of the United States Category:Gymnasts at the 1904 Summer Olympics Category:People from Sandnes
